data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 5.41-acre expanse, this property embodies timeless elegance and historic charm. The home warmly welcomes you with a large, covered porch and natural brick walls that exude rustic authenticity, creating an inviting atmosphere. Two wood-burning fireplaces stand as focal points, providing warmth and infusing a sense of tradition and coziness into the living spaces. The outdoor experience is heightened by a large pond and a screened-in patio, offering an ideal setting for relaxation and social gatherings. A charming three-season room adds versatility and serves as a delightful retreat. The estate further boasts a 4-car garage with space for a workout room or workshop catering to various lifestyle needs. With over 3,000 square feet of living space, four bedrooms, and three full baths, this residence harmoniously blends classic charm with modern comfort, creating a haven that captures the essence of gracious living.
